{"tid":1921728,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《立會初選》合作係本土贏嘅契機","createTime":"2020-03-12T06:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T08:09:29.000Z","uid":321709,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8dbcc321554c762afc45de61d7638d936d135e0a","tid":1921728,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"而家立會初選嘅模式已經逐漸成形<br />\n會係第一階段初選，第二階段協調，第三階段再臨選前退選<br />\n<br />\n本土要贏嘅話，第二階段係契機，而要贏就必須合作<br />\n<br />\n而家基本上每區都有好多本土派參選人，每區嘅選民黎計可以推到一至兩個本土入局（可以睇初選加埋嘅票數決定一定兩個）<br />\n<br />\n所以初選完之後，本土參選人必須願賭服輸，低票嗰d讓路俾高票嗰一兩個本土，然後合作幫佢地拉票<br />\n<br />\n本土今次真係唔可以輸"},{"pid":"4c45c2524b38906ddf0b647471db3cea8a662a73","tid":1921728,"uid":107297,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"本土素人參加初選好過唔參加"},{"pid":"a3a8fcc3b2c249707110313acc49b285ef55000e","tid":1921728,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c45c2524b38906ddf0b647471db3cea8a662a73","tid":1921728,"uid":107297,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"本土素人參加初選好過唔參加"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"係，之前話篩選式個種初選，係對本土素人不利<br />\n<br />\n但而家協調式初選，反而係一個幫本土整合嘅機會"},{"pid":"7ae4790b2e963da0f068ce2f6ed437640b041bfa","tid":1921728,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd32248b3d43b26839992b6cf139bcae2713121b","tid":1921728,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babe0a514e558d2247a94f62c23217661fb60215","tid":1921728,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"個人想法係唔需要擔心初選+立會選舉素人/本